<h2>Mission Statement</h2>
<p>
KCPR strives to provide the Central Coast with a media outlet for students and community members alike to develop, express, and share their passions for music and culture. As a showcase for alternative and diverse programming, the station features eclectic music and local news, creating a unique listening experience.
</p>

<h2>Vision Statement</h2>
<p>
A unique listening experience highlighting local and independent artists, serving the Central Coast by developing and sharing their musical passions.
</p>